\b0 SQL is a very powerful language and is used by nearly every large corporation as their primary database system. However, there are many different versions of SQL that are on the market and are used for different purposes. The SQL command for creating a table is pretty straight forward. Firstly, if using MySQL through PHP My Admin, you will need to begin your development server and then navigate to the PHP My Admin web application. Within the application, you will need to create a database and give it an appropriate name for the project that you are working on. If you have worked on previous projects with PHP My Admin and SQL, there will be a list of all databases that have previously been created. Once the database has been created and submitted, we can now add tables and records to use or manipulate throughout the project.\
